text: Pogonocherus creticus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Kratochvil in 1985. It is known from Crete.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus creticus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1985
